To compile this code on Windows you need to install
* cmake
* mingw-w64
then, you need to open the "build" folder in console
and type
	build-debug.bat
for debug, and
	build-release.bat
for release
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
To compile it on Termux you need to install
* make
* build-essential
* ndk-multilib					//for termux
* ndk-multilib-native-static	//for termux
then, you need to type
	make
for release, and
	make debug
for debug